1
00:01:10,752 --> 00:01:12,431
=Those Days=

2
00:01:12,431 --> 00:01:14,800
(Adapted from iceread.com novel
"You Xi" by Qingyang Wanxi)

3
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,980
=Episode 32=

4
00:01:25,820 --> 00:01:27,640
(Nanzhou Station)

5
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,319
Alright.

6
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,960
Let's stop here.

7
00:01:30,679 --> 00:01:33,080
I won't text my arrival when I get home.

8
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:35,240
No news means I'm fine.

9
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,440
When the insurance pays out,

10
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,000
I'll wire it to you right away.

11
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,319
Text us once you're home.

12
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,559
We'll miss Xiaoqi.

13
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,399
Mingzhu.

14
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:52,479
I'll miss you all very much.

15
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:56,080
Go on.

16
00:01:56,399 --> 00:01:57,679
Go back with your mom.

17
00:02:04,399 --> 00:02:05,399
Add me on WeChat.

18
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,119
(Blood is strange like that.)

19
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,679
(It magnifies love and hate.)

20
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,480
(It softens grudges too.)

21
00:02:14,839 --> 00:02:15,879
(For my father-in-law,)

22
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,240
(Ding Hong)
(they nearly fought.)

23
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,679
(For the child,)

24
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,119
(they stiffened their expressions)

25
00:02:21,279 --> 00:02:23,159
(and awkwardly exchanged WeChat.)

26
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,399
Be good.

27
00:02:28,119 --> 00:02:29,800
Alright, we'll get going.

28
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,119
Take care.

29
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,960
Goodbye.

30
00:02:50,999 --> 00:02:52,480
Text us on WeChat.

31
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,040
(I know)

32
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,559
(going our separate ways)

33
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:03,399
(is inevitable now.)

34
00:03:11,679 --> 00:03:12,439
Shen Minghui.

35
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:16,159
I know you've been streaming lately

36
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,999
and doing pretty well.

37
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,679
But do you realize

38
00:03:22,559 --> 00:03:24,879
your grades and your revenue

39
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,320
are moving opposite ways?

40
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,279
Can't you wait a bit?

41
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,999
Wait till gaokao ends.

42
00:03:30,999 --> 00:03:32,360
Have no burden and go all in.

43
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,439
Wouldn't that be better?

44
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,159
Mr. Hu.

45
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,640
My family needs money.

46
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:41,200
Push through it then.

47
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,040
How do I push through no money?

48
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,080
Mr. Hu.

49
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:46,080
I'll tutor Minghui.

50
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:50,800
Lu Bing.

51
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:53,439
That's also why I called you here.

52
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,240
Here, look.

53
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,480
Your grade
has fallen out of the top five.

54
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,520
If you keep this up...

55
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,599
Mr. Hu, I know.

56
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,279
I'll study harder.

57
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,760
I'll help Minghui too.

58
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,439
That's not my point.

59
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:13,800
Gaokao is right around the corner.

60
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,679
Could you manage yourself first?

61
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,640
You know our school only sends

62
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:20,440
five or six kids to Tsinghua University
and Peking University.

63
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:23,000
One slip and it's over.

64
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,640
Lu Bing.

65
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,320
Mr. Hu.

66
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,200
The way you say it

67
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,839
make it sounds like Lu Bing
is about to become a criminal.

68
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,760
Shut up.

69
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,560
Mr. Hu.

70
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,200
You're a good teacher.

71
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,120
I get everything you said,

72
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,320
but I'm not listening.

73
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,760
I'm a repeat student.

74
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,599
But I'll stick with Shen Minghui

75
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:48,000
even if we can't get into college.

76
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:48,719
No, you...

77
00:04:49,239 --> 00:04:49,960
No, you...

78
00:04:51,919 --> 00:04:52,680
Shen Minghui.

79
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,960
Did you hear that?

80
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,320
Did you hear her?

81
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:57,120
Aren't you moved?

82
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,919
Don't you want to catch up?

83
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,839
To meet a girl like her...

84
00:05:12,039 --> 00:05:13,120
Well... Lu Bing.

85
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,039
Go back to class.

86
00:05:17,039 --> 00:05:18,239
Shen Minghui, stay.

87
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,080
Sit there.

88
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,080
Correct your test answers.

89
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:38,080
(Maybe it's time to be a man)

90
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,279
(and say goodbye with dignity.)

91
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:57,300
(Nanzhou New District People's Court,
Sealed)

92
00:05:59,159 --> 00:05:59,719
Mom.

93
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,239
Let's go home.

94
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,839
Home is always best.

95
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:04,599
Yeah.

96
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,159
Go home.

97
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,960
Careful, Mom.

98
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,239
Here.

99
00:06:30,159 --> 00:06:31,359
Rest a bit first.

100
00:06:31,599 --> 00:06:32,399
I'll cook.

101
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,200
Mingzhu.

102
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:39,120
Our family wronged you.

103
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:42,000
Mom, why bring this up again?

104
00:06:42,919 --> 00:06:44,719
You need to help her with her baby.

105
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,599
It's an honorable job.

106
00:06:47,239 --> 00:06:48,279
Yes.

107
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:52,680
The three of us
will live well from now on.

108
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:53,880
Okay.

109
00:06:54,039 --> 00:06:55,120
And the little one too.

110
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,839
Mom. You have to follow
the chart the doctor gave you

111
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:03,239
and do your physiotherapy properly.

112
00:07:03,239 --> 00:07:03,839
Okay.

113
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,359
No slacking.

114
00:07:05,359 --> 00:07:05,919
Okay.

115
00:07:06,039 --> 00:07:07,039
If you recover earlier,

116
00:07:07,039 --> 00:07:08,839
Meiqi and I can be relieved earlier.

117
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,520
Okay.

118
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,760
Meiqi.

119
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,080
Stay home and take care of Mom for now.

120
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,900
I'm going back to work
at the hotel tomorrow.

121
00:07:14,919 --> 00:07:16,799
We'll each do our part.

122
00:07:17,239 --> 00:07:17,839
Okay.

123
00:07:18,159 --> 00:07:18,760
Okay.

124
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:28,580
(Nanxi Hotel's F&B Department
is closed for renovation.)

125
00:07:37,359 --> 00:07:37,919
Mr. Zhao.

126
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,760
You scared me.

127
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,760
I saw the sign outside saying

128
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,640
the restaurant is closed for renovation.

129
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:45,760
Yes.

130
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,560
What's going on?

131
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:50,479
Mingzhu.

132
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,120
I'll be honest with you.

133
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:53,799
The renovation is fake.

134
00:07:54,479 --> 00:07:55,359
The closure is real.

135
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,399
They're cutting
the whole F&B department.

136
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,520
Everyone's laid off.

137
00:07:59,719 --> 00:08:00,599
Housekeeping

138
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,520
probably won't survive either.

139
00:08:03,039 --> 00:08:05,279
You're pregnant, so you escaped.

140
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,719
At least you still get a minimum wage.

141
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,520
Be grateful.

142
00:08:11,039 --> 00:08:14,159
Go home and take care of the baby.

143
00:08:14,159 --> 00:08:14,799
No.

144
00:08:14,799 --> 00:08:17,159
What about after I give birth?

145
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,520
After?

146
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,159
We'll see then.

147
00:08:20,159 --> 00:08:21,279
Tell me now.

148
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,120
When my maternity leave ends,

149
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:25,719
it'll be my turn to be laid off?

150
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,719
Mingzhu.

151
00:08:30,159 --> 00:08:31,599
I really have no choice.

152
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:50,440
Was this place sold?

153
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:51,680
It didn't sell.

154
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,320
We're here to stick the seals again.

155
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,759
Look.

156
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,119
Isn't it a river-view unit?

157
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,960
I'm telling you, it's quiet at night.

158
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,280
You only hear the water.

159
00:09:19,210 --> 00:09:21,160
You came here
because you need something, right?

160
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:26,400
My workplace is doing mass layoffs.

161
00:09:27,119 --> 00:09:28,759
With our situation at home,

162
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,400
someone has to make money.

163
00:09:31,479 --> 00:09:32,719
So I wanted to ask you

164
00:09:33,359 --> 00:09:35,160
if you could recommend a job for me?

165
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:45,479
One pregnant woman
helping another get a job?

166
00:09:46,719 --> 00:09:49,519
Both of us
taking maternity leave together?

167
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:51,599
Unless the company is run by Buddha,

168
00:09:51,599 --> 00:09:53,519
no one is that generous.

169
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,839
Yeah, I just wanted to ask.

170
00:09:57,839 --> 00:09:58,639
Just in case.

171
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,479
Fine.

172
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,759
I'll keep an eye out for you.

173
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:06,519
See if there's work
without office hours.

174
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,759
Maybe work part-time making slides.

175
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,800
You can make slides, right?

176
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,639
I can.

177
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:17,560
Zhixia.

178
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,999
What happened between you and Hao?

179
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,440
What did you fight about?

180
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,639
You even moved out.

181
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:28,999
My mother-in-law

182
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:32,050
insisted I do an ultrasound
to check if it's a boy or a girl.

183
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:33,879
If it's a boy,
she'll buy a school-zone home.

184
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,160
If it's a girl, she won't.

185
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:38,359
Well...

186
00:10:38,359 --> 00:10:41,359
I'm telling you, Mingzhu,
this is a thorn in my side.

187
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,639
Because my mom favors boys,

188
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:45,479
Xu Zhidong comes to me
for every little thing.

189
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,519
Because my grandma favored boys,

190
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:49,599
they gave you away.

191
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,719
I'm sorry.

192
00:10:55,599 --> 00:10:57,639
It's fine. It's all in the past.

193
00:10:59,170 --> 00:11:00,759
I don't know if you really moved past it

194
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:01,639
or if you're just saying it.

195
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:03,519
But I haven't gotten over it.

196
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:05,519
Are my mom and grandma bad people?

197
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,200
No.

198
00:11:06,999 --> 00:11:08,280
Did they treat us badly?

199
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,119
No.

200
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,920
My mom thinks about me and you

201
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,639
every day.

202
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,040
My grandma really

203
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,920
held on to dear life,

204
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,320
waiting for you to come back.

205
00:11:16,599 --> 00:11:17,960
But when it mattered most,

206
00:11:17,970 --> 00:11:20,280
I'm the one who suffered,
and you're the one who was abandoned.

207
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,479
All because we were girls.

208
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,359
I don't get it.

209
00:11:23,359 --> 00:11:25,040
I really don't get it.

210
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,999
So no matter the baby I'm carrying

211
00:11:26,999 --> 00:11:28,400
is a boy or girl,

212
00:11:28,719 --> 00:11:30,359
I will never let Jiaojiao

213
00:11:30,359 --> 00:11:32,239
feel confused the way I did.

214
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,719
Pregnant women can't get mad.

215
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:41,400
Here, have a candy.

216
00:11:42,119 --> 00:11:43,359
Add some sweetness to life.

217
00:11:47,479 --> 00:11:48,879
Just skip the chili.

218
00:11:48,999 --> 00:11:49,560
Okay.

219
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:51,280
I know you love spicy food.

220
00:11:55,999 --> 00:11:56,519
Hao, you...

221
00:11:56,839 --> 00:11:57,839
She's pregnant.

222
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,639
Why did you take so long?

223
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:03,200
My old scooter went around half the city
to pick up Chen.

224
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,400
You were rushing me,

225
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,879
so I switched to a fast ride.

226
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:06,650
It was fast enough.

227
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:07,719
What's going on?

228
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,920
Things are extremely bad.

229
00:12:10,060 --> 00:12:11,119
I've been here many times.

230
00:12:11,119 --> 00:12:12,119
She won't leave with me.

231
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,320
So I figured you two could help talk to her.

232
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,040
Why us?

233
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,060
My sister listens to me?

234
00:12:18,119 --> 00:12:19,200
She won't listen to you.

235
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,639
But we can each grab a side

236
00:12:21,719 --> 00:12:23,080
and carry her out.

237
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,280
Bichen's here too.

238
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:26,519
Use tactics?

239
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:27,400
Use tactics.

240
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,440
My workplace pays me the minimum now.

241
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:34,080
I don't even know
if they're paying insurance.

242
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,200
They are for sure.

243
00:12:36,719 --> 00:12:38,440
You're pregnant. You're the priority.

244
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,839
Feels like a special privilege.

245
00:12:44,479 --> 00:12:45,280
- Zhixia.
- Hao.

246
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,280
Zhixia.

247
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,160
Zhixia.

248
00:12:47,999 --> 00:12:48,639
Hao.

249
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:49,999
Mingzhu is here too.

250
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,200
Zhixia.

251
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:52,800
Come home with me.

252
00:12:54,359 --> 00:12:56,400
Why are you all here together?

253
00:12:56,479 --> 00:12:57,999
I don't have discounted eggs.

254
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,040
Zhixia.

255
00:12:59,479 --> 00:13:01,239
We're here to take you home.

256
00:13:01,599 --> 00:13:02,680
You're pregnant.

257
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,680
Stop making a fuss.

258
00:13:04,239 --> 00:13:05,680
Xu Zhidong, whose side are you on?

259
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,239
Do you even know what's going on?

260
00:13:07,239 --> 00:13:10,180
I'm making a fuss? What did I do?
Who did I bother? Did I invite you here?

261
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:13,599
See? Why talk to her like that?
Who did she bother? What did she do?

262
00:13:13,599 --> 00:13:14,639
Did she invite you here?

263
00:13:15,999 --> 00:13:16,599
Zhixia.

264
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,479
Give Hao a chance

265
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:19,800
for Jiaojiao's sake.

266
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:20,479
Zhixia.

267
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:21,839
Go home with Hao.

268
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:23,719
If someone came to pick me up,

269
00:13:23,719 --> 00:13:25,320
I'd run faster than a rabbit.

270
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:33,879
Come home.

271
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,479
Jiaojiao misses you.

272
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,200
She's losing weight missing you.

273
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,879
I'm not using our kid as leverage.

274
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:39,839
This home

275
00:13:40,639 --> 00:13:41,759
can't work without you.

276
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:46,239
It can't work without you.

277
00:13:46,479 --> 00:13:46,960
Yes.

278
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:48,800
Trying to abduct me?

279
00:13:52,999 --> 00:13:53,800
Depart.

280
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,719
I'm not carrying the crown prince.

281
00:13:57,839 --> 00:13:59,320
Mingzhu. Let's have a meal together.

282
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,359
Hao will pay for it.

283
00:14:00,359 --> 00:14:01,000
- No.
- Yes.

284
