393
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:37,319
Shen Minghui, stop bragging. Come on.

394
00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:38,440
Hit another one and show me.

395
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,200
Hit me again.

396
00:18:40,239 --> 00:18:41,120
Calm down.

397
00:18:51,079 --> 00:18:52,400
