399
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:54,960
A slop bucket.

400
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:57,319
He's an 18 or 19 years old.

401
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,600
What about his pride?

402
00:18:59,079 --> 00:19:00,400
Gaokao's coming up!

403
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,440
