404
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,600
You think he's like him?

405
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:03,850
Repeating senior year for five years?

406
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,719
Xiaobo's dad, calm down.

407
00:19:05,719 --> 00:19:06,680
You have to trust us.

408
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,600
We'll handle this properly.

409
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:09,719
Handle?

410
00:19:09,799 --> 00:19:10,519
I'm telling you

411
00:19:10,519 --> 00:19:11,640
He must be expelled.

412
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:12,999
No.

413
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:13,999
Xiaobo's dad.

414
00:19:14,640 --> 00:19:15,200
Xiaobo...

415
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,279
Xiaobo's dad.

416
00:19:18,279 --> 00:19:19,239
Calm down.

417
00:19:19,479 --> 00:19:20,840
Trust the school.

418
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,079
Come in.

419
00:19:43,479 --> 00:19:44,279
Mr. Hu.

420
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:45,920
I'm sorry.

421
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:48,239
What good is apologizing to me?

422
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:49,880
How about this?

423
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,840
Apologize to Fan Xiaobo properly.

424
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,200
We'll smooth things over
with his parents.

425
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,079
I'm not apologizing.

426
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,400
He deserved it.

427
00:19:57,479 --> 00:19:59,640
Didn't you hear what his dad said?

428
00:19:59,719 --> 00:20:00,840
He wants you expelled.

429
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:02,200
Expel me then.

430
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,200
Are you out of your mind?

431
00:20:05,479 --> 00:20:06,759
Gaokao is coming up.

432
00:20:06,759 --> 00:20:08,759
Life isn't only about gaokao.

433
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:11,239
But yours is about to end.

434
00:20:11,319 --> 00:20:12,680
Hang in there just a bit more.

435
00:20:12,680 --> 00:20:13,880
And you'll finish it.

436
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,960
I've already tried gritting my teeth.

437
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,840
My mock 3 results
were worse than mock 2.

438
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,840
My mom forced me
to study at Nanzhou High

439
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:22,999
for five years already.

440
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,200
Mr. Hu.

441
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:31,120
I watched you grow up.

442
00:20:32,999 --> 00:20:34,759
