443
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:36,120
Shen Minghui.

444
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,759
You need confidence.

445
00:20:37,759 --> 00:20:39,719
You just haven't figured it out yet.

446
00:20:39,759 --> 00:20:40,479
Hu Gang.

447
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:42,759
Can you not lie through your teeth?

448
00:20:43,279 --> 00:20:44,759
Shen Minghui hasn't figured it out?

449
00:20:44,799 --> 00:20:45,960
Can't you see?

450
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:46,880
He set this up.

451
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,400
He even got you involved.

452
00:20:52,479 --> 00:20:53,239
Shen Minghui.

453
00:20:53,479 --> 00:20:54,519
Tell me the truth.

454
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:56,680
Did you fight on purpose
to get expelled?

455
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,239
Speak.

456
00:20:58,719 --> 00:20:59,600
None of your business.

457
00:21:03,239 --> 00:21:03,840
I...

458
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,440
You...

459
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:09,880
What?

460
00:21:10,999 --> 00:21:11,880
You got expelled?

461
00:21:13,999 --> 00:21:15,400
I never wanted to study anyway.

462
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,440
Isn't this great, Dad?

463
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,079
You brat!

464
00:21:19,759 --> 00:21:20,759
Shen Minghui!

465
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,200
Are you looking for trouble?

466
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,160
How could you?

467
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:25,519
How could you?

468
00:21:25,519 --> 00:21:27,239
Are you trying to

469
00:21:27,239 --> 00:21:28,999
