I can do other things.

475
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:43,120
You're quite proud, aren't you?

476
00:21:43,999 --> 00:21:45,400
Go get me a rope.

477
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,840
You can't even go one day

478
00:21:48,999 --> 00:21:51,400
