491
00:22:29,759 --> 00:22:30,400
Let's go.

492
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:39,200
Go.

493
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:42,880
Careful, watch the steps.

494
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:43,719
I'm fine.

495
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,160
Do you regret it?

496
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:32,559
Regret?

497
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:35,160
Following your wife is never wrong.

498
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,960
