502
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,079
Dad, Mom.

503
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,079
You're back.

504
00:24:16,210 --> 00:24:17,519
Dad, what happened to your hand?

505
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,039
