515
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,650
No one could talk him into it.

516
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:39,999
No one could talk him into it.

517
00:24:40,039 --> 00:24:41,680
You spoiled him.

518
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:44,680
