00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:15,760
You're fine? Hurry.

850
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,519
- Sit.
- Okay.

851
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:18,079
Good people are blessed.

852
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:19,119
Yes.

853
00:40:19,119 --> 00:40:19,760
Sit.

854
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,360
Mrs. Feng.

855
00:40:20,559 --> 00:40:21,599
Try the meatballs later.

856
00:40:21,760 --> 00:40:22,840
Taste my cooking.

857
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:23,840
Sure.

858
00:40:25,119 --> 00:40:26,639
Don't bother.

859
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:28,039
Here, have some tea.

860
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:30,079
Meiqi.

861
00:40:35,199 --> 00:40:36,720
We're here to pay you back.

862
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,999
No, what's this for?

863
00:40:39,079 --> 00:40:39,760
Thank you.

864
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,159
What's this for?

865
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:42,720
Thank you.

866
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:01,880
Mr. Zhao.

867
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:04,360
Mingzhu.

868
00:41:04,599 --> 00:41:05,440
Why are you here?

869
00:41:06,159 --> 00:41:07,720
I called you so many times.

870
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:08,720
You didn't answer.

871
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,440
I was in a meeting just now.

872
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:12,920
Maybe I couldn't pick up.

873
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:15,360
I know you're avoiding me on purpose.

874
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,440
But I really need this job.

875
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:20,159
I know that once my maternity leave
ends, I'll lose this job.

876
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,760
Can you help me?

877
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,679
Even if you come back now,
there's no job.

878
00:41:23,679 --> 00:41:26,199
There's no position available.
And you're pregnant.

879
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,199
I'm pregnant, not sick.

880
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:29,159
I can work.

881
00:41:29,159 --> 00:41:31,559
I can handle any department and any job.

882
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,400
Okay, I understand your situation.

883
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:36,159
Let me check
with the higher‑ups first. Alright?

884
00:41:36,159 --> 00:41:37,150
Let's leave it at that for now.

885
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:37,920
Mr. Zhao.

886
00:41:38,559 --> 00:41:40,360
When can you give me an answer?

887
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:43,159
I really need this job.

888
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,240
I need the money.

889
00:41:48,039 --> 00:41:48,679
Mingzhu.

890
00:41:49,639 --> 00:41:50,880
Let me be honest with you.

891
00:41:51,639 --> 00:41:54,199
The hotel is currently
full of old employees.

892
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,240
Business is bad, the burden is heavy.

893
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:59,440
The themed wedding you did
before did well,

894
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:01,599
but that's just a drop in the bucket.

895
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:03,199
It doesn't solve the real problem.

896
00:42:03,199 --> 00:42:04,400
I can keep doing it.

897
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,599
I can scale it up.

898
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,800
The restaurant's too old-fashioned.

899
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,390
The wiring is aging.

900
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:10,920
There's a short circuit every few days.

901
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:12,440
The ceiling is about to fall apart.

902
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,920
They're all safety hazards.

903
00:42:14,119 --> 00:42:15,679
If something goes wrong,

904
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,559
we'll pay more than we earn.

905
00:42:18,119 --> 00:42:19,880
Then I can go to another department.

906
00:42:20,060 --> 00:42:21,360
I have an accounting certificate.

907
00:42:21,519 --> 00:42:22,320
I can do finance.

908
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:23,240
Mingzhu.

909
00:42:24,159 --> 00:42:26,559
Everyone's cutting costs
and raising efficiency now.

910
00:42:26,999 --> 00:42:29,320
Who's going to hire a pregnant woman?

911
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:30,880
You won't be able to work for long.

912
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,240
You'll go on maternity leave soon.

913
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:34,720
So what if I'm pregnant?

914
00:42:35,999 --> 00:42:38,280
Wasn't everyone born by a mother?

915
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,910
Why is it that the moment I'm pregnant,

916
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:43,229
nobody wants me anymore?

917
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,950
♪The world is noisy♪

918
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,930
♪Turning around,
it's already a distant view♪

919
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,230
♪Once I didn’t know what to do♪

920
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:05,310
♪What to hold quietly♪

921
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:08,260
♪Like a silent care♪

922
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:12,530
♪Seasons pass by♪

923
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:15,390
♪Time ticks away♪

924
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,790
♪Seems like I understand a little♪

925
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,570
♪And also let go of some things♪

926
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:24,290
♪All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth♪

927
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:27,780
♪A long letter is written down♪

928
00:43:27,930 --> 00:43:31,410
♪Gently spreading love♪

929
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:35,600
♪To all the forks in fate♪

930
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:41,230
♪Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved♪
